  "title": "Westminster Shorter Q62",
  "body": "What are the reasons annexed to the fourth commandment?\n\nThe reasons annexed to the fourth commandment are, God's allowing us six days of the week for our own employments, his challenging a special propriety in the seventh, his own example, and his blessing the sabbath-day.",
